and leisure in the Zhang family.

26
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,410
But what about them?

27
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:11,120
They don't have a life left to live.

28
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:13,680
Jiu

29
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:17,180
was a little demon
of the raccoon dog demon clan,

30
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:17,980
900 years old.

31
00:03:18,310 --> 00:03:20,280
Because of its love for food and fun,

32
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,940
it accidentally cultivated
into a great demon.

33
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,870
