34
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,960
one human and one demon.

35
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:36,520
They were once locked in a cage
and dunked in water.

36
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,290
The wife, a water-snake demon,

37
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,150
broke off her tail

38
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:44,960
to help her husband escape.

39
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:50,690
Qiu Hanlin,

40
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:52,750
a young master from a noble family

41
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,210
and Fuying's benefactor.

42
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,030
Fuying took human form

43
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,690
upon hearing his flute.

44
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,200
And it's not just these demons
I mentioned.

45
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,650
Many humans and demons in the village

46
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,910
don't have a future anymore.

47
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,430
And all of this

48
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,150
was because of me.

49
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,680
Do you still think

50
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,360
I can go back with you?

51
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,040
I understand.

52
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,310
But Zhang Qi,

53
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:46,430
Yiqi Alliance already knows

54
