what happened in Peach Village.

55
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:53,390
This is the Ximen family's territory.

56
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:55,650
They won't allow Peach Village to exist.

57
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:58,670
Even if the Ximen family
doesn't kill them,

58
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,480
they're weak beings

59
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,560
