62
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:13,600
Tonight as I sit here,

63
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:15,750
I've cursed myself countless times

64
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,080
for being deceived by Qingli

65
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:20,920
and causing everyone's death.

66
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,950
How foolish

67
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,040
and unforgivable.

68
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:26,830
