87
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,480
Starting tomorrow,

88
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:30,040
the miasma will once again
shroud Dingling Mountain.

89
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,480
All paths leading to Peach Village

90
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,430
will be cut off.

91
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:34,360
The Ximen family

92
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,240
will never enter again.

93
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,270
