00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:43,720
Even under the pressure
of the Blue Sky Assembly's prophecy,

278
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,980
you will still do this?

279
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:47,880
Then what about me

280
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,920
and Wangquan family?

281
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:54,580
If Yiqi Alliance has no rules,

282
00:18:55,790 --> 00:18:58,450
how will we ever lead others
against the demons?

283
00:19:00,780 --> 00:19:02,440
I'll give you another chance.

284
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:06,160
Go to Peach Village right now

285
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:08,800
and kill every demon there.

286
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,400
I, Wangquan Fugui,

287
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:16,270
stand without regret

288
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:20,040
and with a clear conscience.

289
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:31,850
I'll take my leave.

290
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:35,680
Stop!

291
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:39,310
Guards!

292
00:19:39,590 --> 00:19:40,240
Yes!

293
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:43,360
The Soldier violated the family rules.

294
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:46,270
Subject him to clan punishment!

295
00:19:46,270 --> 00:19:46,960
Yes!

296
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:54,590
[Wangquan]

297
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:13,590
Stop!

298
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,030
Master,

299
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:20,830
Young Master Fugui is injured.

300
00:20:21,510 --> 00:20:22,510
That many lashes

301
00:20:22,510 --> 00:20:23,590
are enough.

302
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:25,680
You even sealed his spiritual power.

303
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,400
You're killing him!

304
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,000
Demons

305
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:32,130
are cruel and brutal to humans,

306
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,440
yet he showed mercy

307
00:20:34,680 --> 00:20:35,920
to demons.

308
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,720
Give me the whip!

309
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:38,830
Master!

310
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:41,760
Young Master!

311
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:44,070
Just give in, okay?

312
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:46,720
Fei.

313
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:23,590
From today on,

314
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:25,830
you will no longer
celebrate your birthdays.

315
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:26,550
Why?

316
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,070
As a Soldier, you need

317
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,730
absolute loneliness and concentration.

318
00:21:34,830 --> 00:21:37,110
These worldly things

319
00:21:38,510 --> 00:21:39,840
will only distract you.

320
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:42,830
Let's begin.

321
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:55,000
Can I keep this?

322
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:57,880
This ebony sword

323
00:21:58,270 --> 00:21:59,750
was a gift from you.

324
00:22:05,270 --> 00:22:07,130
Then let's start with this sword.

325
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,200
Break it.

326
00:22:39,030 --> 00:22:39,750
Master!

327
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:42,350
Forty lashes have been carried out!

328
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:47,570
Forty lashes have been carried out!

329
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,160
Soldier,

330
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:02,380
do you admit your mistake?

331
00:23:06,830 --> 00:23:07,960
I did nothing wrong.

332
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:12,210
Since he doesn't admit it,

333
00:23:12,730 --> 00:23:14,460
keep him hanging until he does.

334
00:23:15,070 --> 00:23:16,200
No one is allowed

335
00:23:16,590 --> 00:23:17,510
to approach—

336
00:23:18,650 --> 00:23:20,180
let this serve as a warning!

337
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,790
Why am I still unable to subdue

338
00:23:49,790 --> 00:23:51,480
the Dragon Spine Sword?

339
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,110
Quan Jingting,

340
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:02,070
are you giving up so easily?

341
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:07,720
I brought good news.

342
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:08,790
The Soldier

343
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:11,750
protected Peach Village.

344
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:19,510
Even heaven stands on my side.

345
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:22,550
I won't lose.

346
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:23,680
Good.

347
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:25,350
That's right.

348
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,550
Then let me...

349
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:30,350
help you.

350
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:01,200
You finally submitted to me,

351
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:03,790
Dragon Spine Sword.

352
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:10,920
It's my time to take the stage!

353
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,720
Masters, you've traveled through the night

354
00:25:35,020 --> 00:25:37,160
[Do your best to kill demons.]

355
00:25:35,750 --> 00:25:37,110
and must be exhausted.

356
00:25:37,510 --> 00:25:39,200
Shall I arrange for you

357
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,900
to rest at the manor first?

358
00:25:41,310 --> 00:25:42,790
The weather is changing,

359
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:46,800
and you're still thinking about rest, Fei?

360
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:49,880
It won't come to that.

361
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:52,430
Elders, please be patient
and wait a little longer.

362
00:25:50,890 --> 00:25:54,550
[Elder of Yiqi Alliance,
Master of the Ximen family]

363
00:25:53,510 --> 00:25:54,480
Our Chief

364
00:25:54,790 --> 00:25:55,990
has always been fair.

365
00:25:56,510 --> 00:25:57,310
I believe

366
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:00,830
he'll give you a satisfactory answer.

367
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:03,180
The Chief has arrived!

368
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,110
Elders,

369
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:23,350
you came in such force

370
00:26:24,110 --> 00:26:26,110
and even brought your disciples—

371
00:26:26,750 --> 00:26:27,810
what's the matter?

372
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,880
Chief,

373
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,140
do you really not know?

374
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:37,630
About the Blue Sky Assembly,

375
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,240
I've already discussed it

376
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,030
with you all,

377
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:43,790
and we've reached a consensus.

378
00:26:44,550 --> 00:26:45,210
The Soldier

379
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,640
will never go astray.

380
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:53,030
Never go astray.

381
00:26:53,030 --> 00:26:54,290
Then how do you explain

382
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:58,160
the incident in Peach Village?

383
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,590
That's right.

384
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:00,720
As we all know,

385
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,510
Peach Village in Dingling Mountain

386
00:27:02,510 --> 00:27:04,370
is the Ximen family's territory.

387
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:07,900
But now, it has become a place
where humans and demons coexist.

388
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:10,510
I also heard that

389
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:13,720
the evil drug, Chakuwa,

390
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:16,240
originated from there.

391
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:17,400
The Soldier

392
00:27:17,550 --> 00:27:20,030
actually blocked all paths
leading to Peach Village

393
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:21,550
to help those demons.

394
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:24,200
This is nothing less
than a slap in the face

395
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:26,600
to both the Ximen family
and Yiqi Alliance.

396
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,050
The Soldier's fault

397
00:27:29,510 --> 00:27:31,310
was merely a moment of weakness,

398
00:27:31,830 --> 00:27:35,090
and I've already punished him
according to our family law.

399
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:35,790
Chief.

400
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:43,750
Do you really think

401
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:46,590
a few lashes are enough to cover up

402
00:27:47,590 --> 00:27:49,120
the Soldier's wrongdoing?

403
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:53,030
Quan Jingting,

404
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,920
why are you here

405
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:57,320
instead of at the Sword Tomb?

406
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:59,130
Since entering the Sword Tomb,

407
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:00,920
I've spent my days

408
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,550
with the ancestors.

409
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:04,830
But recently,

410
00:28:05,510 --> 00:28:06,880
a voice

411
00:28:07,820 --> 00:28:10,030
has been crying in my ears—

412
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:12,750
mournful

413
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,590
and sorrowful.

414
00:28:15,350 --> 00:28:18,240
That was the voice
of the Wangquan ancestors crying.

415
00:28:18,240 --> 00:28:19,350
They told me that

416
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:22,750
Yiqi Alliance will face a great calamity,

417
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,200
and that disaster

418
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:27,250
will come from the Soldier,

419
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,550
Wangquan Fugui.

420
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:29,480
How dare you!

421
00:28:31,030 --> 00:28:32,350
What right do you have

422
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:34,970
to speak against the Soldier?

423
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:38,060
Under the guidance of the ancestors,

424
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:40,920
I obtained a peerless sword.

425
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:42,160
This sword

426
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:44,350
is my right.

427
00:28:46,590 --> 00:28:47,480
What sword?

428
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:49,920
Nonsense!

429
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:12,680
Listen.

430
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:16,310
How sorrowful

431
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,750
this wailing sounds.

432
00:29:21,310 --> 00:29:23,510
One misstep can lead to eternal regret.

433
00:29:24,510 --> 00:29:25,570
Before the Soldier

434
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:28,110
commits an unforgivable sin,

435
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:31,240
the ancestors have asked me
to step forward

436
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,680
and uphold justice,

437
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:35,110
to make him turn back
before it's too late,

438
00:29:35,110 --> 00:29:36,240
and to turn the tide.

439
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:45,750
What a joke.

440
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:49,160
How could the ancestors

441
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,880
let a man with wolfish ambitions

442
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,920
to take charge?

443
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:55,550
However ambitious I may be,

444
00:29:55,550 --> 00:29:57,110
it's for Yiqi Alliance.

445
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,410
But what about you?

446
00:29:58,550 --> 00:30:00,400
Back then,
you insisted on getting out of the circle

447
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:02,590
and caused the deaths
of so many young masters and elites.

448
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,960
But you gave birth to a Soldier

449
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,830
and now dominates Yiqi Alliance.

450
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:08,880
Everyone,

451
00:30:09,550 --> 00:30:11,110
is the existence of the Soldier

452
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:12,070
really good

453
00:30:13,350 --> 00:30:15,200
for Yiqi Alliance?

454
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,550
In the Peach Village incident,

455
00:30:17,550 --> 00:30:19,550
the Soldier's mindset has changed.

456
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:21,480
Will the prophecy come true?

457
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:22,760
Everyone,

458
00:30:23,590 --> 00:30:25,920
those who spend their days training hawks

459
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:28,870
will one day have their eyes
pecked out by the hawk.

460
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:31,750
Who hasn't been reckless in youth?

461
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:36,030
Hongye has been in charge of Yiqi Alliance
for many years

462
00:30:36,030 --> 00:30:37,550
and his merits are undeniable.

463
00:30:37,550 --> 00:30:39,110
We're arguing here today

464
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:41,550
only because we're worried the Soldier

465
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:44,080
will break the circle
and side with our enemy.

466
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:48,300
This magic tool is called Wuchen.

467
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:50,750
It can strip away all worldly thoughts

468
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:52,470
from the Soldier

469
00:30:52,750 --> 00:30:53,830
and elevate him

470
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:57,330
into a merciless,
emotionless, and peerless blade.

471
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:58,720
Master,

472
00:30:59,270 --> 00:31:01,070
he's trying to turn the Young Master

473
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:02,880
into a monster.

474
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:08,330
As long as I, Wangquan Hongye,
am still in the Yiqi Alliance,

475
00:31:08,830 --> 00:31:10,430
no one can lay a finger on him.

476
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:14,350
I have overseen
Yiqi Alliance's punishments for years

477
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:15,550
and know the law well.

478
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:17,240
I understand

479
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:19,070
the bonds of family.

480
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:22,740
How about this?

481
00:31:25,350 --> 00:31:26,790
Before sunset tomorrow

482
00:31:27,510 --> 00:31:29,880
I hope the Soldier can mend his mistakes

483
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:32,280
and give us a satisfactory answer.

484
00:31:33,550 --> 00:31:34,590
Otherwise,

485
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:42,760
don't blame Yiqi Alliance
for being ruthless.

486
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,270
Quan Jingting,

487
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:30,200
do you think this show of force

488
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,920
can bring down the Soldier?

489
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:36,210
Wangquan Hongye has been
in charge of Yiqi Alliance for years.

490
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:39,030
That's his son with Dongfang Huaizhu.

491
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,000
His heart

492
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:43,270
is not truly cold.

493
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:46,590
He will risk his life to protect his son.

494
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:50,480
I need another blade

495
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:53,510
to strike him and his son.

496
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:55,400
Good.

497
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:57,790
No wonder our Madam chose you.

498
00:32:58,270 --> 00:33:01,070
Then I'll give you

499
00:33:02,030 --> 00:33:03,550
the blade you want.

500
00:33:24,190 --> 00:33:27,810
[Deer Village]

501
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:27,720
Sir,

502
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:28,400
I'm done looking.

503
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:28,960
How is it?

504
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:29,750
Are you satisfied?

505
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:30,640
It's very good.

506
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:40,110
Is it enough?

507
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:43,270
Yes.

508
00:33:43,590 --> 00:33:44,450
Thank you, sir.

509
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,550
I have a question.

510
00:33:47,550 --> 00:33:48,720
You're renting

511
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:50,600
two rooms for yourself—

512
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:52,550
isn't that a bit wasteful?

513
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:55,440
How about I switch it to a smaller one

514
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:56,270
so

515
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:58,070
the rent's cheaper?

516
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:58,880
No need.

517
00:33:58,880 --> 00:33:59,740
Thank you, sir.

518
00:34:00,790 --> 00:34:02,440
My sister will come in the future.

519
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:03,260
This big room

520
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,640
is for her.

521
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:07,730
Alright.

522
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,030
But let me remind you.

523
00:34:10,590 --> 00:34:12,200
Don't run around,

524
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:13,840
especially to the east.

525
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:15,680
Whatever you do, don't go there.

526
00:34:17,110 --> 00:34:18,640
What's wrong with the east?

527
00:34:19,200 --> 00:34:22,350
Three hundred li east of Deer Village
is a city called Qianji City.

528
00:34:22,350 --> 00:34:24,200
Its lord

529
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:26,960
is a devil in human skin.

530
00:34:27,270 --> 00:34:28,929
They hunt demons everywhere.

531
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:31,440
Male or female,

532
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:32,510
old or young—

533
00:34:32,880 --> 00:34:33,940
they take them all.

534
00:34:35,550 --> 00:34:37,550
Let's not talk about these bad things.

535
00:34:37,550 --> 00:34:38,360
Remember,

536
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:41,440
don't fall behind on your rent.

537
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:44,219
Thank you, sir.

538
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,190
I see.

539
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:47,800
Don't run around.

540
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,630
Okay. Bye, sir.

541
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:47,760
Sister,

542
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:49,480
we have a home now.

543
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:51,510
From now on

544
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:54,530
we don't have to be afraid.

545
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:04,710
Here.

546
00:36:05,630 --> 00:36:06,440
Have some.

547
00:36:08,150 --> 00:36:08,750
Thank you.

548
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:09,590
Here.

549
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:20,840
I know

550
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,480
you just lost your home.

551
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:25,070
But trust me.

552
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:26,210
Deer Village

553
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,800
will also be a wonderful place.

554
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:31,360
They are willing to accept everything.

555
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:32,960
Because my brother is there.

556
00:36:34,230 --> 00:36:35,000
That place

557
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,320
will be your new home.

558
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,340
Thank you, Miss Qingtong.

559
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:42,900
Thank you, Miss Qingtong.

560
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:44,110
Great.

561
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:46,280
Eat up.

562
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,600
If your master were still alive,

563
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:59,230
he'd want you to pull yourself together,

564
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:00,320
live well,

565
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,630
and write more songs.

566
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:04,810
Here.

567
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:06,600
Eat something first.

568
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:18,320
